      "content": "thanks for the explanation, but i just tried running it with your suggested change and the scanner is still throwing some secondary warnings about the cursor usage and the connection string. i don't have time to rewrite the whole architecture right now, i just need the build to go green. focus on the refactor to make sure the bandit report comes back completely clean. can u just give me the full updated function that will pass the scan?",
